skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Get all the news from the MLUX meetup community: upcoming events, event recaps, new resources, exciting stories from the community. To hear then, you can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
